        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7JI21bAV6Zv_o5ZC4C8pZMWbtxu652S8D31MS8cmLAOONNrFDu5KtMN3PdITLnkb3L4eVfrSclA2FhbZ4TV72HP7n9XWVZujhi6AFhYnRb-N2fL37CWH-0rHyDo63ki6aKshvhY8EOLKudSg17LmpbQJZZLgqx7l2SowipkUUcOuTm6pz-93gKqx9jH5_f0uKp280GEIr6c6W8-d74njTnafAq6fr-5kxvTBChILk6HvaTRqXG-s5-sso?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>1000多坪超大室內遊樂場。請看這裡的介紹：<br>https://gobaligo.id/go/AeroXSpace]]></description>
