      <Placemark>
        <name><![CDATA[Clip 'n Climb Bali]]></name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5g93TV-2VjP9ylyQIm5fssc_4JSGBc9pR4bwt3Fi8_pzpMWepA3LLBbySWV3aJzfLLTqDPV07B0MhiujsA_V1_ZUk9zwo4wq9GyNCacqA7Vn3ngI-XYPs14hq7wL7NBeNT3XMlq2P-B1gpsRKMW82jcGCsxIz_VoRuSfXhmEKgQHoFon9tl_n-lE1qbaqc02jVYl4KWh7mAePXM5kE2qv-qv3jQjNsPwbV7tch1ePWUXHbkPORfcIO5Po?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>世界知名的Clip 'n Climb室內攀岩中心來到峇里島啦！<br>詳細介紹及優待票券：<br>https://gobaligo.id/go/clipnclimb_sanur]]></description>
